An embodiment of the invention discloses a data flow type transmission method and a device thereof, which is applied for group network containing a HTTP proxy server, wherein the data flow type transmission method comprises the following steps: receiving the data blocks which are from a hypertext transfer protocol HTTP proxy server by a terminal; storing the data blocks in a broadcasting sequence by the terminal; and broadcasting the data blocks sequentially by the terminal in the broadcasting sequence in a time period after a first data block is stored and before the last data block is stored. According to the embodiment of the invention, the terminal can realize the data flow type transmission in a special group network comprising the HTTP proxy server when the HTTP is used as a base.
