The invention discloses a terminal content adaptation method and a device thereof. The method comprises the following steps: acquiring a capability property and a network capability property of a terminal; and adapting downloaded information according to the acquired capability property and the acquired network capability property of the terminal. Meanwhile, the embodiment of the invention also provides a terminal content adaptation device. The device comprises an acquisition module for acquiring the capability property and the network capability property of the terminal, and an adaptation module for adapting the downloaded information according to the acquired capability property and the acquired network capability property of the terminal. The method and the device help adapt the downloaded information according to the acquired capability property and the acquired network capability property of the terminal, and send the adapted information to the terminal, which facilitates users to quickly browse clear information which is most suitable for use.
