The invention discloses a terminal split-screen display method and a device thereof. The method comprises the following steps: identifying a format of acquired information; sorting the identified information according to the format; and performing a split-screen display on the sorted information. Meanwhile, the embodiment of the invention further provides a terminal split-screen display device which comprises an identification module for identifying the format of the acquired information; a sorting module for sorting the different formats of the acquired information which is identified by the identification module; and a display module which is used for the split-screen display of the information sorted by the sorting module. Compared with the prior art, the terminal split-screen display method and the device have the advantages of ensuring the maximum reading comfort of users and really reading according to demands.
