The embodiment of the invention discloses a data reading method and a device thereof. The data reading method comprises the following steps: reading current data from a network; judging whether the current data are provided with follow-up data; storing the follow-up data in a cache from the network if the following data are provided; and reading the follow-up data from the cache. By the method and the device, the waiting time before users open and browse information is reduced, and the use experience of a user is improved.

